                <p>Make sure errors follow the guidance in <a href="/patterns/error-message/">error message</a> and have specific error messages for specific error states.</p>
                <p>GOV.UK Design System has <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/text-input/">some great examples of tried and tested error messages.</a></p>

